WEBVTT

00:08:59.088 --> 00:09:00.853
I have a friend named Olu.

00:09:00.877 --> 00:09:02.472
He's 35 years old.

00:09:02.496 --> 00:09:06.441
His parents, born in Nigeria,
came to Germany on scholarships.

00:09:06.465 --> 00:09:10.026
Olu was born in Nuremberg
and lived there until age 10.

00:09:10.050 --> 00:09:12.843
When his family moved to Lagos,
he studied in London,

00:09:12.867 --> 00:09:14.292
then came to Berlin.

00:09:14.316 --> 00:09:16.975
He loves going to Nigeria --

00:09:16.999 --> 00:09:19.633
the weather, the food, the friends --

00:09:19.657 --> 00:09:22.171
but hates the political corruption there.

00:09:22.655 --> 00:09:23.855
Where is Olu from?

00:09:24.426 --> 00:09:26.617
I have another friend named Udo.

00:09:26.641 --> 00:09:28.148
He's also 35 years old.

